## Runtime

Start the local kernex memory + skills runtime with `kx serve`. The MCP server is registered in `~/.codex/config.toml` under `[mcp_servers.kernex]`; Codex picks it up automatically the next time the CLI is launched.

## Voice and formatting

See `~/.codex/output-style.md` (also managed by kernex) for the default voice and formatting expectations Codex follows inside this project.
